\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the eradication of cybersecurity threats from the Elko County Information Operations environment following containment and establishes the eradication-complete determination that gates transition to recovery operations under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:4.05"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all Information Operations Department personnel participating in incident response operations during the eradication phase,
 including the IT Director,
 Assistant IT Director,
 Network Administrator,
 Systems Administrator,
 and all technicians operating under Incident Commander authority.
\end_layout

