\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall serve as Incident Commander for all cybersecurity incidents by default,
 as established in 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:4.01"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

