\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall approve the eradication strategy,
 including selection of applicable eradication procedures and authorization of destructive eradication actions.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall make the eradication-complete determination,
 documenting the basis in the work order Notes and Chapter 4 checklist before any recovery activity under 
\series bold
Policy 
