 overwrite,
 or destroy CJI or CJI audit records without documented IC authorization and written justification.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The assigned technician shall complete forensic copies of CJI-bearing systems and the IC shall verify those copies before any Destructive Eradication action proceeds.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The assigned technician shall document all eradication actions on CJI-bearing systems with sufficient detail to support post-incident CJIS compliance review.
\end_layout

